{"tid":1537343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[你班仆街身有屎系列] 調查元朗襲擊3個動議　元朗區議會全部否決","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:34.000Z","uid":121683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bcf4fa56f6e5ef063efc0376c59c380516139ea","tid":1537343,"uid":121683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2443359?fbclid=IwAR0ThyPQbZvGaYVg58Y1a3oHTrrUFXvxqMhIvc1rIFaPct2BfWkbbHPAu7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2443359%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ThyPQbZvGaYVg58Y1a3oHTrrUFXvxqMhIvc1rIFaPct2BfWkbbHPAu7M&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3PsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=6dd90295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2443359?fbclid=IwAR0ThyPQbZvGaYVg58Y1a3oHTrrUFXvxqMhIvc1rIFaPct2BfWkbbHPAu7M</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗西鐵站7月21日晚上發生白衣人無差別襲擊事件，造成45人受傷。元朗區議會於今（3日）合併討論721元朗暴力襲擊事件，其中有議員動議要求成立獨立調查委員會，惟遭過半數議員反對，3個有關調查721元朗無差別襲擊案的動議均遭否決。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議會黃偉賢議員就元朗721無差別襲擊事件，在會議上動議要求成立獨立調查委員會，其中包括支持監警會徹查各界對警察的各項指責及成立對話平台等。議案最終以7票贊成、22票反對、2票棄權否決有關動議。<br />\n<br />\n其中贊成的議員包括：陳美蓮、杜嘉倫、黃偉賢、麥業成、李月民、鄺俊宇以及湛家雄；而反對的議員則包括鄧家良、楊家安、袁敏兒、梁明堅、鄧慶業、鄧卓然、蕭浪鳴、陸頌雄、鄧焯謙、姚國威、劉桂容、文美桂、文家駒、黃煒玲、馬淑燕、呂堅、梁福元、梁志祥、鄧鎔耀、郭強、趙秀嫻及程振明；陳思靜及王威信表示棄權。<br />\n<br />\n而李月民議員動議要求成立「檢討721元朗西鐵站暴力事件」的工作小組，議案最終以8票贊成、20票反對、3票棄權否決有關動議。<br />\n<br />\n其後，黃偉賢議員針對元朗白衣人無差別襲擊市民，再次動議成立檢討小組，最終以5票贊成、22票反對、2票棄權，再次否決動議。"},{"pid":"4ae7e5b16df8b3d85fc003f26a5bfb48d53b09d1","tid":1537343,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc58b486a64a5996ccc287f8d501c0b2ba444fab","tid":1537343,"uid":158718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yw7R37Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYw7R37Z.jpg&h=56753a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提提你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得9.7係全民㩒錢日！"},{"pid":"0d0eacff56d576e796d060b558fd0e5c96dacb94","tid":1537343,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}